{"tid":1121177,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美小學把2女童退學　校方解釋：妳媽通姦","createTime":"2019-04-23T07:12:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T01:48:15.000Z","uid":130626,"like":51,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ffc868a88bd27b096acc93cbaec38b3eff2a4795","tid":1121177,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T07:12:45.000Z","msg":"美國俄亥俄州薩米特郡（Summit County）的一間基督教私立小學，上周五（19日）把一名未婚媽媽的2名女兒退學，要求兩人在30天內轉校。校方解釋，這名媽媽未婚，且2名女童有不同的生父，證明她「通姦」。由於學生入學時，家長都有簽署操守承諾，她的行為已違反協議。對此，這名未婚媽媽痛批學校︰「不應該因為這些理由，影響孩子的教育。」<br />\n家住阿克倫（Akron）的女子格蘭特（Summer Grant）育有2名女兒（小學二年級和四年級）。她聲稱，教堂山基督教小學（Chapel Hill Christian School）的員工指責她「活在罪惡中」，所以開除她女兒。<br />\n根據對話錄音，學校行政牧師威爾遜（John Wilson）向格蘭特稱：「學校強烈建議家長應該結婚，學生也應該是同一名父親所生」。他又警告︰「通姦有違十誡。你的女兒不是不應該上學，而是不能夠就讀我們學校。」格蘭特又指，去年7月威爾遜就曾在家長會上，問她為何兩個孩子有三個父親（各自的生父，及格蘭特目前的同居人）。<br />\n威爾遜與學校教育委員會不願詳談此事，只發表聲明稱，格蘭特的錄音並不完整；同時強調，家長曾簽署行為、操守準則協議，協議是出於基督教誨，而學校一向關注學童「感情及心靈上的安全」，把2人退學，是為了保護學校兒童、其他家長的必要行為。<br />\n格蘭特希望學校能改變主意，她說︰「基督徒不應該斷定他人，也不該因此影響孩子的教育。」她又補充，兩名女兒是因為考取獎學金而就讀私校，現在一時之間也沒辦法轉到公立學校。「女兒們沒有可以去的學校了，我不知道該怎麼辦。」（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190423/640_8c7292e598145b6efc8543eb6aa1249d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190423%2F640_8c7292e598145b6efc8543eb6aa1249d.jpg&h=f86f8a6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190423/640_b545cb05034312a68b2ab476d28232ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190423%2F640_b545cb05034312a68b2ab476d28232ad.jpg&h=f26e6546&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n格蘭特。 翻攝《abc News》<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190423/640_05d60a40d8373e69b45a534b2d097753.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190423%2F640_05d60a40d8373e69b45a534b2d097753.jpg&h=7354bca6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190423/640_452404fbb2b867e1c787f03c66f6e203.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190423%2F640_452404fbb2b867e1c787f03c66f6e203.jpg&h=83d0dce5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n學校行政牧師威爾遜。 翻攝《教堂山基督教小學》<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190423/1554985/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190423%2F1554985%2F&d=%2FIqeUsS3N0qecbTP5cC9OG8HdWgMvHIPJs6XZvMXZMw%3D&h=8cc96b6c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190423%2F1554985%2F&h=86f5df9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190423/1554985/</a>"},{"pid":"8119fd8b8f5f7e5315ff952879788165d175c48b","tid":1121177,"uid":69568,"like":11,"dislike":8,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T07:20:08.000Z","msg":"抵啦 2年換兩個經手人 分分鐘係公廁嚟"},{"pid":"5ac30489820712c5b4cec2405f33647a6324027f","tid":1121177,"uid":57462,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T07:21:24.000Z","msg":"咁如果有違佢既辦學宗旨，又好似冇錯。<br />\n唔係間間學校都有教無類架嘛。"},{"pid":"2b82058014b95679d0d43b98a8eef99ea4f0cb18","tid":1121177,"uid":220431,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T07:22:30.000Z","msg":"簽署操守承諾，她的行為已違反協議。"},{"pid":"f6e905b599f54c2a1bceb5f6499d2af04368bf7a","tid":1121177,"uid":60655,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T07:22:33.000Z","msg":"1屋4姓既由來"},{"pid":"432db7642fae55b4e46790bbfc537afae8873b0d","tid":1121177,"uid":196924,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T07:35:21.000Z","msg":"由於學生入學時，家長都有簽署操守承諾，她的行為已違反協議。<br />\n<br />\n自己簽完仲批評人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0ac75933368ff36f5b78aec642c2bf40a459fe6","tid":1121177,"uid":60057,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"cite